name: Advance
description:
Life is about progress, its about changes, Entering 2022 we meet new life expectation. So much plan that we arrange ahead of us, but so little things we manage to finish. By this message i encourage all of us to keep advancing towards your goals and dreams, aim higher! Every little step take you closer to finish. And if you willing enough, help others reach their goals and gain together. Life won't wait for you, it will always keep moving. Because Life is Advance.

Keys : B G D A B G D A

Audio and Visual by Faozato
